{"id":29645773299,"name":"Run api tests","node_id":"WFR_kwLOA_1uaM8AAAAG5waZ8w","head_branch":"feat/userdetails-soft-refresh-v2","head_sha":"df3f015f73d14cb9b6db219ebdf7aec53a0f5ded","path":".github/workflows/run-api-tests.yml","run_number":51196,"run_attempt":1,"event":"pull_request","display_title":"feat: soft-refresh UserDetails via authz epoch and generation stamps","status":"completed","conclusion":"success","workflow_id":5591308,"check_suite_id":80284232468,"check_suite_node_id":"CS_kwDOA_1uaM8AAAASsVArFA","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29645773299","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29645773299","pull_requests":[{"id":4082416672,"number":24493,"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/pulls/24493","head":{"ref":"feat/userdetails-soft-refresh-v2","sha":"a1636ab82d0a579dbd175a491cc01354259cf9fb","repo":{"id":66940520,"name":"dhis2-core","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core"}},"base":{"ref":"master","sha":"c3320e59d5bec49c56be7c49b497585e42695325","repo":{"id":66940520,"name":"dhis2-core","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core"}}}],"created_at":"2026-07-18T13:14:02Z","updated_at":"2026-07-18T13:26:51Z","run_started_at":"2026-07-18T13:14:02Z","jobs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29645773299/jobs","logs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29645773299/logs","check_suite_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/check-suites/80284232468","artifacts_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29645773299/artifacts","cancel_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29645773299/cancel","rerun_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29645773299/rerun","head_commit":{"message":"feat: soft-refresh UserDetails via authz epoch and generation stamps\n\nReplace role/user-driven mass SessionRegistry.expireNow with a JDBC-backed\ntwo-level invalidation scheme:\n\n- authz_version table holds per-user ('user', \u003cuid\u003e) and per-role\n  ('role', \u003cuid\u003e) generation stamps plus a single global epoch row; every\n  bump advances the epoch in the same transaction as the entity change,\n  so readers can never observe a stamp without its data. A schema-only\n  JPA mapping (AuthzVersion) lets H2 test contexts generate the table;\n  production schema stays Flyway-managed (V2_44_16) and validated at\n  startup.\n- UserDetailsSoftRefreshFilter (session-bound auth only: form + OIDC,\n  never JWT/PAT/stateless, never during impersonation) checks one epoch\n  read per request; on epoch movement it compares the principal's\n  effective generation and lazily rebuilds an immutable UserDetails\n  snapshot, replacing the Authentication with an explicit\n  SecurityContextRepository save. No logout, no cookie change.\n- AuthzService memoizes snapshots per username keyed by a pre-read epoch\n  (stamp-before-build invariant) with striped single-flight rebuilds;\n  JWT and PAT auth paths share the same epoch-validated cache.\n- Role authority/restriction edits and role deletion bump one role key,\n  O(1) regardless of member count. User role/org-unit changes and group\n  membership deltas (import hook owning side + service paths) bump only\n  affected users.\n- Gen bumps are update-first with a dialect-branched first-insert\n  (Postgres ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING; plain INSERT on H2, which has no\n  ON CONFLICT support).\n- Password change, disable, lock, and expiry keep hard session\n  invalidation.","author":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"msvanaes@dhis2.org"},"id":"df3f015f73d14cb9b6db219ebdf7aec53a0f5ded","tree_id":"81e714a70e4fee3b31b1ee9bf09d3c99c3f35c79","timestamp":"2026-07-18T13:13:29Z","committer":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"msvanaes@dhis2.org"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/5591308","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0